Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.21,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,ashita he tsuzuku sakamichi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:32.51,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,surechigau otona tachi wa tsubuyaku no sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.64,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,"ai toka yume toka risou mo wakaru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.81,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me no mae no genjitsu wa sonna ni amaku nai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.15,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,tsumazuki nagara mo korogari nagara mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:55.36,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kasabuta darake no jyounetsu wo wasuretaku nai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.83,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,otona ni narenai bokura no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.33,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,tsuyogari wo hitotsu kiite kure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.54,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,nige mo kakure mo shinai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.46,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,waraitai yatsu dake warae
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.25,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,semete tayori nai bokura no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.80,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,jiyuu no me wo tsumitoranai de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.80,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,mizu wo ageru sono yakume wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.89,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,hataseba iindarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.21,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,On the uphill road that leads to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:32.51,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We pass by adults who tell us this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.64,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,"I can understand ideals such as love and dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.81,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,but the real world isn't as easy as you think"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.15,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Even though we keep tripping and falling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:55.36,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We have to remember these pains of growing up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.83,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,For all of us who can't force ourselves to do so yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.33,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Listen to this one thing I have to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.54,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I won't run or cower away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.46,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,So whoever wants to laugh at me, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.25,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Since we can't be relied upon yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.80,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Don't take away our seed of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.80,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,The task of nurturing this plant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.89,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,That's all we have to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Intro}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Zonisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rashirudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. You're fighting seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already prepared myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For having to battle\Nstrong guys like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuzonisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be a kind ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, there's\Nonly one thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. To defeat those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're determined to come at us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:38.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs55\pos(488,495)}Endless Fight to the Death\NGash vs Bali
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end it with one strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. So they continue to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their final struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the human who\Nreceived my blow after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So this human is not\Nintimidated by Bali's punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Looks like they still\Nthink they can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after receiving your blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will seriously beat them to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy... he still has so much power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give them our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga... he blocked it with his fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuzonisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're flying up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're escaping to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They've come after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bit early to be falling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you able to withstand my attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Impertinent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash, above you! Shoot up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Dodged, at that range?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! As if such a move\Ncould hit me when I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Zonisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Their attack missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro, counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor crumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance to attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...is done like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigano Zonisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead is good enough.\NAn escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... let this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let this... anything but a direct hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:03.13,Note,,0,0,0,,Flag says "Tsuchinoko" which is a mythical animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the spot Gash was at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I think... there was a chimney\Nsomewhere around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange... I'm\Nsure it was around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh, this is! A track\Nleft by a tsuchinoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's still fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you little... I'm going first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he didn't get\Nwhat he was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why am I so annoyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With each enemy I defeat, I\Ncome closer to being king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is something missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I defeat\Nthem, I am unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, my irritation grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigano Zonisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I fought these guys,\Nmy irritation would be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But these guys were the\Nsame as all the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? They're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot lose here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose, I cannot become a kind ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that wish... I will\Ndefinitely make it come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,End it with the next shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Baou Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They are still able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zorushirudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, demon? Even you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Baou Zakeruga had no effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet... My irritation is not yet relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Baou Zakeruga is our\Nmost powerful attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, he took a direct hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet... how is he standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Worthless. Is that the limit, for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After using Baou Zakeruga,\Nmy body won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't use any more spells.\NNot even a single Zakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro. You've got to hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected. Looks like that's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't give me\Nwhat I wanted either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that we have\Nno more business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zonisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy!\NActually blocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'm striking first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Such an insolent move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eyes of Gash...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there. In that shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, I'll fight on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let them touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. When my strength\Nreturns, I'll back you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, we can take\Nthis a step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move towards becoming\Na kind ruler one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Koruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we had a kind ruler,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we wouldn't need to\Nfight such a terrible battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A kind ruler?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Koruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will survive and win\Nthis battle. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become a kind ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do that, Gash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become a kind ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I won't give up.\NAfterward, I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. They ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Up for this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy, he's after my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to give me that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You really want me to finish you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy... He's trying to\Ncollapse the ceiling on top of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... Stupid thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to move anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind. I still have an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still able to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you. Hand over the\Nbook already! Do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let you pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I... cannot... let you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Still talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... my body refuses to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro must rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am still able to keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up and die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand stopped again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why am I frightened of his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened by this worn out little kid,\Nwho can't use any more spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You said your name was Gash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of ruler are\Nyou striving to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A kind ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. That is the kind of path it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you let an\Nunimportant thing escape earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,was to hold straight to your ambition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, you put yourself\Nat a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you wish to be a kind ruler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the only type of king I could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bali, what kind of ruler\Ndo you wish to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You just defeat the\Nenemies in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You, who only believes in\Nthe ideal of a hooligan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...cannot defeat his\Neyes of true aspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A kind ruler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to admit\Ndefeat to this little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Bali... I will ask you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of ruler will you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A strong one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who my opponent is, I will\Nsilence him with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A strong ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One who will lose to no one,\Nthe strongest king!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. That is a notch higher\Nthan a mere hooligan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash. And Kiyomaro, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will let you go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your "kind ruler" or my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is more suited to be the new\Nking will be revealed eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That book... I will leave it intact for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the strong ruler,\Nwhat must I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good fighting like before,\Nwithout a thought, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. You must contemplate\Na lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I will contemplate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This has begun to get interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Bali got what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro and Gash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you my gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for giving Bali an opportunity to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But do not forget, I could have\Nburned your book at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You two must grow even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us meet again. I shall look\Nforward to our next encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll help with the rest...\NI'll teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I mean,\N"I'll do something about it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:12.62,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Stars atarashii mirai e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.46,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,akiramenai hitori janai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.88,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,mou mayowanai yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.89,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me no mae no genjitsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.90,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,he kon de shimau koto hoshi no kazu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.78,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yuugure no aka wo mita
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.78,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku ni hitsuyou na kawaranai yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.70,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku wa boku de kimi wa kimi no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.83,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yuzurenai jounetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:04.59,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me wo sorasazu ni tatakai tsuzukeru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.22,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,We've gotta take the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:14.68,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,sorezore no nido to nai toki wo kizamou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.81,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,shinjitsu wa Rhythm Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.61,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,toki no nagare ni makenaide arukou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.82,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:12.62,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Stars, to the new tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.46,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't give up, you are not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.88,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I have no more doubts, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.89,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,to the truth before my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.90,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,to the things I give in to, the number of stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.78,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I saw the redness of evening
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.78,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,the unchanging courage that I need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.70,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,me and mine, you and yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.83,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,unyielding passion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:04.59,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't turn your eyes away, continue to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.22,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We've gotta take the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:14.68,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,try to carve the moments that won't come again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.81,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,truth is Rhythm Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.61,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't lose to the flow of time, walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.82,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of person\NUmagon's Book Keeper is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! At last we've found\Nthe Book Keeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Konjiki no Gash Bell:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Umagon! Critical danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to work together\Nand deliver the presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:04.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs60\bord3\pos(488,495)}Meru Meru Mee!\NUmagon Critical Danger?!

